# Windsurf Rules — xgh (eXtreme Go Horse)

Full agent instructions: see `AGENTS.md` at the repository root.

## Project type

Bash/YAML/Markdown MCS tech pack. No compiled artifacts. No npm/cargo/maven build step.

## Core rules

- Read `AGENTS.md` before starting any task
- Test-first: write a failing `bash` test in `tests/` before implementing
- All bash: `#!/usr/bin/env bash` and `set -euo pipefail`
- Track tasks with `- [x]` checkboxes in `docs/plans/`
- No secrets in source — environment variables only

